snippet.textDisplay: im a healthy and fit 50 year old. no jabs. worked throughout all lock downs as a construction worker come into contact with people from all over the world on every site and im struggling to come to terms with the fact that i and my fellow co workers from latvia to london from portugal to paddington didnt become ill from this pandemic. none of us. hundreds of us. how?
